wesctww_tests tests vawious wesctww functionawities and intewfaces incwuding
both softwawe and hawdwawe.

Cuwwentwy it suppowts Memowy Bandwidth Monitowing test and Memowy Bandwidth
Awwocation test on Intew WDT hawdwawe. Mowe tests wiww be added in the futuwe.
And the test suit can be extended to covew AMD QoS and AWM MPAM hawdwawe
as weww.

wesctww_tests can be wun with ow without ksewftest fwamewowk.

WITH KSEWFTEST FWAMEWOWK
=======================

BUIWD
-----

Buiwd executabwe fiwe "wesctww_tests" fwom top wevew diwectowy of the kewnew souwce:
 $ make -C toows/testing/sewftests TAWGETS=wesctww

WUN
---

Wun wesctww_tests as sudo ow woot since the test needs to mount wesctww fiwe
system and change contents in the fiwe system.
Using ksewftest fwamewowk wiww wun aww suppowted tests within wesctww_tests:

 $ sudo make -C toows/testing/sewftests TAWGETS=wesctww wun_tests

Mowe detaiws about ksewftest fwamewowk can be found in
Documentation/dev-toows/ksewftest.wst.

WITHOUT KSEWFTEST FWAMEWOWK
